Title: D-brane Thickness

Authors: H. Arfaei and M.M. Sheikh-Jabbari

Comments: Tex, 9 pages, No figures, we have some changes in the text

The scale in the D-brane theory is discussed from different points of view.It is shown that scattering of a $D_4$-brane by a $D_0$-brane gives thecondition to penetrate beyond the string scale.